(432, 1, '<div><img alt="xolo A600 image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/all/themes/xolo/images/xolo-a600-sidelogo-new.png" /></div>\r\n<div>XOLO has released a new but a very good looking device for just 8000/-(Approximately).Here are some quick specs to check out!!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img title="xolo A600 processor" alt="xolo A600 processor image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/default/files/xolo-a600-processor.png" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>1.3 GHz Dual Core Processor</h3>\r\nRun as many applications as you want, swiftly and smoothly. The 1.3 Ghz Dual Core processor delivers impressive performances on every front.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img title="xolo  A600 Display" alt="xolo  A600 Display image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/default/files/xolo-a600-display.png" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>11.43 cm (4.5) qHD IPS Display</h3>\r\nLarge 11.43 cm screen for comfortable viewing with qHD IPS display for crisp and sharp imagery. With its big and brilliant display, turn your device into an entertainment zone for movies, pictures and everything else!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img title="xolo  A600 Camera" alt="xolo  A600 Camera image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/default/files/xolo-a600-camera.png" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>5 MP Rear Camera</h3>\r\nCapture beautiful shots with its 5 MP auto focus rear camera. Use its VGA front camera for 3G video calling.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img title="xolo A600 battery " alt="xolo  A600 battery image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/default/files/xolo-a600-battery.png" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>1900 mAh Battery</h3>\r\nForget about recharging your phone before you hit home, XOLO A600 is loaded with large 1900 mAh battery that lasts long and lets you do more with your device.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img title="xolo A600 Jelly Bean" alt="xolo  A600 Jelly Bean image" src="http://www.xolo.in/sites/default/files/xolo-Jelly-Bean-a600.png" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Jelly Bean v4.2</h3>\r\nWith Android OS Jelly Bean 4.2, switch between home screens and apps at the flick of a finger.\r\n\r\nFull Detailed Specs:\r\n<table width="100%" border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="3" align="center" valign="middle">XOLO A600</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="4" align="center" valign="middle">Network</td>\r\n<td rowspan="2" align="center" valign="middle">Frequency Bands</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">GSM 850/900/1800/1900</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">HSPA 2100</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="2" align="center" valign="middle">HSDPA/HSUPA</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">up to 21 Mbps (DL)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">up to 5.6 Mbps (UL)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="2" align="center" valign="middle">Processor</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Chipset</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">MT 6572W</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">CPU</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">1.3 GHz Dual Core</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Graphics core</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Chipset</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Mali-400 MP</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="7" align="center" valign="middle">Design</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Dimensions</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">136 x 67 x 9 mm</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="2" align="center" valign="middle">Hard Keys</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Power key</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">Volume key</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="4" align="center" valign="middle">Slots</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">SIM card slots (2)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">micro USB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center" valign="middle">micro SD Card slot</td>\r\n</tr>\r\