(651, 1, '<p style="text-align: left;">Ubislate 7CX is the high-end tablet from Datawind.Its priced at Rs3999.Its the first tab under 5k with 7 inch display and also with EDGE and GPRS connectivity.Its one of the successful running tablet in the market.Datawind has made its recognition in the world for its low cost tablets.It runs on Android 4.0.4 with 512MB of RAM making it seamless in Multi-tasking.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Here is a quick look for the specifications of the tablet:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Specifications of Datawind UbiSlate 7CX Tablet (2G Calling, 3G via Dongle, 2 GB)</h3>\r\n<strong>General</strong>\r\n<table cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Brand</td>\r\n<td>Datawind</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Model ID</td>\r\n<td>UbiSlate 7CX</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>SIM</td>\r\n<td>Single SIM, GSM</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>SIM Size</td>\r\n<td>Mini SIM</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Processor</td>\r\n<td>1 GHz Cortex-A8</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Graphics</td>\r\n<td>Mali-400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Voice Call</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Supported Networks</td>\r\n<td>2G: GSM 900, 1800; 3G: UMTS 2100</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>In The Box</td>\r\n<td>Charger, Tablet, Data Cable, Micro USB Converter</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>Platform</strong>\r\n<table cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Operating System</td>\r\n<td>Android 4.0.4 (Ice Cream Sandwich)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>Memory</strong>\r\n<table cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>RAM</td>\r\n<td>512 MB DDR3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>\r\n<table cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Internal Storage</td>\r\n<td>2 GB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Expandable Storage Capacity</td>\r\n<td>32 GB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Memory Card Slot type</td>\r\n<td>microSD</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong>Display</strong>\r\n<table cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>